    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<i>BATHYSPHERE</i>》是一款在深海狭小潜水球中展开的恐怖策略冒险游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角为了寻找失踪的人而踏入这片深海。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在深海中展开一场回合制的生死游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与你的敌方潜水球互相发射探测波，并根据回传的讯号推断对方位置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有先击落敌人的人，才能继续活着深入更深处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192130/extras/da349c299c032f5630252dcf590c5723.poster.avif?t=1772069143\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192130/extras/da349c299c032f5630252dcf590c5723.webm?t=1772069143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192130/extras/da349c299c032f5630252dcf590c5723.mp4?t=1772069143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >神秘设施与时间循环</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里究竟发生了什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用失败带来的洞察，以及从诡异设施中获取的情报，逐渐扩大你的理解范围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切都会重置，但知识不会消失。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192130/extras/2e862b02b768a4a1f46cb8342f40902a.poster.avif?t=1772069143\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192130/extras/2e862b02b768a4a1f46cb8342f40902a.webm?t=1772069143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1940年代的模拟深海探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜水球内堆满了独特的模拟设备与纸本文档。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调节广播频率，阅读手册，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跨越时间被隐藏的秘密正等着你揭开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192130/extras/ca43e0844811cff78ed106b52e85e788.poster.avif?t=1772069143\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192130/extras/ca43e0844811cff78ed106b52e85e788.webm?t=1772069143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192130/extras/ca43e0844811cff78ed106b52e85e788.mp4?t=1772069143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
